Wanted - WANton Text EDitor
===========================


Description:
-----------
Wanted is a text editor written in Python/Tk for a didactical purpose by a team
of inexperienced developers. The primary scope is to learn python language and
team developing. At the beginning we choose to implement only basical text
editing let functionalities growing up in future releases.


